law.history: Repealed 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 121, sec. 46, effective June 19, 1958. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 84, sec. 65, effective July 1, 1953. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 681c-17.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Appointment of director as attorney for society for service of process; provisions for service.
